scenes.description: Oozora Subaru performs the song "Hoshiairi" at her 6th Anniversary Live.
Ending credits roll with a highlight reel of the live performance.

subtitles.english: No matter how far, we'll keep running through it all

subtitles.english: Even if we get hurt, I want to be laughing tomorrow

subtitles.original: 間違いも いつかのための正解でしょ？
subtitles.english: Even mistakes are the right answers for some future time, right?

subtitles.original: 色褪せたこの世界で 繰り返していくだけの毎日
subtitles.english: In this faded world, every day is just a repeat of the last

subtitles.original: 言えずにいた言葉を 風に乗せてひとり呟いた
subtitles.english: I whispered the words I couldn't say into the wind, all alone

subtitles.original: 素直になるためには まだまだ勇気が足りないけど
subtitles.english: I still don't have enough courage to be honest

subtitles.original: 水しぶきあげて飛び込んだ 目を瞑りながら
subtitles.english: But I dove in, making a splash, with my eyes closed

subtitles.original: 悪天候に虹を描いて 青く塗りつぶした
subtitles.english: Drawing a rainbow in bad weather, painting it all blue

subtitles.original: 扉開けて飛び出そうよ はじめましての未来へ
subtitles.english: Let's open the door and jump out to a future we've never seen before

subtitles.original: どこまでも 僕ら駆け抜けていくんだ
subtitles.english: No matter how far, we'll keep running through it all

subtitles.original: 傷ついて傷ついたって 明日は笑っていたいな
subtitles.english: Even if we get hurt, I want to be laughing tomorrow

subtitles.original: 間違いも いつかのための正解でしょ？
subtitles.english: Even mistakes are the right answers for some future time, right?

subtitles.original: 顔上げて走り出そう ひとりぼっちがふたりで
subtitles.english: Look up and start running, two lonely souls together

subtitles.original: 転んだって泣いたって 不器用でいいじゃん さあいくんだ
subtitles.english: Even if we fall or cry, it's okay to be clumsy. Come on, let's go!

subtitles.original: 何が正解で不正解かも ときどきわからなくなって
subtitles.english: Sometimes I lose track of what's right and what's wrong

subtitles.original: 涙堪えながら 答えを探し続けていたんだ
subtitles.english: Holding back my tears, I kept searching for the answer

subtitles.original: 溢れた涙 見つけた笑顔 全部宝箱にしまって
subtitles.english: The tears that spilled, the smiles I found, I'll put them all in a treasure chest

subtitles.original: いつか立ち止まったら 思い出してまた笑いたいな
subtitles.english: If I ever come to a stop, I want to remember them and laugh again

subtitles.original: 満天の星空を描いて 願い事をしよう
subtitles.english: Let's draw a sky full of stars and make a wish

subtitles.original: 流れ星も描き足そうか 僕次第で変われるんだ

subtitles.original: いつまでもこの日々が続くといいな

subtitles.original: 望んだって叶わない ことだらけでも悪くないな

subtitles.original: 明日へとこの歌が届くといいな
subtitles.english: I hope this song reaches into tomorrow

subtitles.original: 手を取って笑い合って ありのままを描いていくんだ
subtitles.english: Holding hands and laughing together, we'll draw it just as it is
